ACADEMIC INTEGRITY CLAUSE
==============================================================================

This software is an original educational project developed for academic 
purposes. While this project is made publicly available as open source 
software, it is specifically PROHIBITED for any student or participant 
enrolled in the same academic course, class, or educational program for which 
this project was originally developed to:

1. Copy, fork, or clone this repository for submission as their own work
2. Use substantial portions of this code in their coursework submissions
3. Replicate the architecture, features, or implementation details for 
   academic credit in the same course
4. Present this work, in whole or in part, as their own original creation

Violations of this clause constitute academic dishonesty and may result in 
disciplinary action according to the policies of the relevant educational 
institution.

